trans-unit.source: üëã Welcome to TelegramDB Search Bot. This bot allows you to find public channels and groups, and see what public chats a user is in, or has been in, using a constantly updated database with 300+ million chats and 1 billion users! Use our inline queries to get user details from usernames and IDs. üÜì Free commands: /resolve [id or username] - Resolve a username or ID /search [name] - Search for groups and channel /group [name] - Search for groups /channel [name] - Search for channels /bot [name] - Search for bots /add [username] - Add a user to TelegramDB üí≤ Premium commands: /where [id or username] - Find groups in which a user has been /members [id or username] - Find members of a group /near [id or username] - Find nearest users /network [id or username] - Find nearest chats /credits - Buy credits ‚Ñπ Other commands: /faq - Frequently Asked Questions /language - Choose the language /support - Support chat for TgDB /stats - Show statistics /terms - Terms and conditions /cancel - Cancel current operation For any info or doubts join @tgdbchat

We are not Telegram, we can only answer questions related to TelegramDB!
Join @tgdbchat or write to @tgdb_support for TelegramDB.org support.
